 <title>FedRAMP from a Project Manager&#039;s Perspective</title>
 <link>/drupal-govcon-2016/drupal-govcon-2016/sessions/fedramp-project-managers-perspective</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;So you’ve just found out that your Government Agency is moving their portfolio to FedRAMP – Now What?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This session is built from lessons learned by a PM in the FedRAMP trenches. It will discuss what to expect, offer ways to increase your chances of project success, and will shed a light on changes that go along with the FedRAMP territory.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By attending this session the audience will gain:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;a view into the FedRAMP project landscape&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;a sense of the changes that come with moving to FedRAMP &lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;strategies for increasing chances for success&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;ways to prepare yourself as a Project Manager&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;This session is designed to offer tools that will help you plan your FedRAMP implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-experience field--type-list-text field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Experience level:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-speakers field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;mlow&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-session-timeslot field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Session Time Slot(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;entity entity-field-collection-item field-collection-item-field-event-timeslots clearfix&quot; class=&quot;entity entity-field-collection-item field-collection-item-field-event-timeslots&quot;&gt;
